{"type": "article", "id": 30225, "title": "用回收塑料制成的两用包", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-27T22:59:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160727215012ev6wjb0APnSq8xNs.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>单从外观来看，这款名为 Hamilton Perkins 的拎背两用包和市面上同类产品并没有什么太大的区别，但它所使用的原材料可能会让你惊叹于它的环保程度：整体采用回收的塑料瓶制成，内衬所使用的乙烯基塑料则来自废弃的广告牌，因此每一个包都是独一无二的。所有两用包均在位于海地的工作坊加工生产，这种特殊的制作模式不仅降低了二氧化碳的排放，也为当地人提供了工作机会。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/26334503/hamilton-perkins-collection-from-plastic-bottles-t/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 95 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607272150307qBcEs2wDkuAJMH3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727215029P9mGa1bMtUYurKCW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664706\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607272150306g3vEYZU1PkWNHzc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727215030ZRjObL5G0zh2k3dF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}